msgid "{avatar} heard a hidden clue in the market rumors of {location}: {fragment}"
msgstr "{avatar}在{location}的坊市流言中聽聞一段隱秘線索：{fragment}"

msgid "{avatar} glimpsed a corner of the truth through a mysterious insight: {fragment}"
msgstr "{avatar}於冥冥感悟中窺見一角真相：{fragment}"

msgid "{avatar} noticed an unusual clue at {location}: {fragment}"
msgstr "{avatar}在{location}察覺到一段異樣線索：{fragment}"

msgid "{avatar} connected scattered clues and finally learned a world secret capable of shaking this realm's foundations."
msgstr "{avatar}將零散線索連成一線，終於知曉了一樁足以動搖此界根基的世界秘密。"

msgid "{avatar} has pieced together scattered clues and learned a world secret capable of shaking this realm's foundations. If revealed, the secret will become known to all under heaven; if kept silent, only {avatar} will bear it. Complete secret: {secret}"
msgstr "{avatar}已經憑藉零散線索知曉一個足以動搖此界根基的世界秘密。此秘密若公開，會成為天下共識；若沉默，則只有自己承受。完整秘密：{secret}"

msgid "Reveal the world secret?"
msgstr "是否公開世界秘密"

msgid "You have learned a secret capable of shaking the world's foundations. Will you tell all under heaven, or remain silent alone?"
msgstr "你已知曉一個足以動搖世界根基的秘密。要將它告知天下，還是獨自沉默？"

msgid "Tell everyone"
msgstr "告訴所有人"

msgid "Reveal the complete secret so all cultivators under heaven know this realm's truth."
msgstr "將完整秘密公之於眾，使天下修士皆知此界真相。"

msgid "Bear it silently"
msgstr "默默承受"

msgid "Do not spread it; bear this truth alone."
msgstr "不主動傳播，只由自己承受這份真相。"

msgid "{avatar} revealed a world secret to all: '{title}'. From now on, cultivators under heaven know this realm's truth."
msgstr "{avatar}將一樁世界秘密公之於眾：「{title}」。此後天下修士皆知此界真相。"

msgid "{avatar} chose silence after learning the truth, pressing this secret deep into the heart."
msgstr "{avatar}知曉真相後選擇沉默，只將這樁秘密壓在心底。"
